 />\n<br />\n你睇返鐘意韓國既人都多左 裝扮係韓風既"},{"pid":"fdabd10a5ac28c147739cac83dfdee48cb4e6641","tid":2508961,"uid":27312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"曾經香港音樂同香港電影都係韓國威過<br />\n<br />\n宜家就真係風水輪流轉"},{"pid":"a097e124d828d3c0b435857b5e90a83867ed8839","tid":2508961,"uid":277992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"靠 供三小"},{"pid":"1ac8138f4b24603cdc52155d343dafb3babcd600","tid":2508961,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"下雨天留客天留我不留"},{"pid":"a2cc3f11686f3b215119a753a1200a290aa130d1","tid":2508961,"uid":247847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7585e4c0b2b2d6d42e5cd3fda7ddda684d0f80da","tid":2508961,"uid":230821,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4dcdb2e214d67954846acd6c4fc06a68eb184a99","tid":2508961,"uid":247847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de30611b0706ae9502ba40a1f9726cb09b5065a4","tid":2508961,"uid":230821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"成日都見到 有冇搞錯 打廣東話啦屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:44:59.000Z","msg":"例子？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"用書面語加埋啲 幹啦 你娘 三小 等等嘅嘢 唔用廣東話口語"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"流行文化帶動好正常<br />\n<br />\n香港都受多日本等亞洲各國詞語影響，明明叫豬肉又寫豚肉，韓國的部隊鍋，oppa等<br />\n<br />\n再者學校一定教書面語為主，廣東話詞彙要去到大學當文化一類去探究，好多口語點寫都未必好多人識<br />\n<br />\n香港人最多咪打同音字，打千秋，山卡啦果d，正寫記鬼到咩"},{"pid":"6e5634442d81b4c140f706ce4a2d4b55ed9a9073","tid":2508961,"uid":230821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /